{"type": "article", "id": 6333, "title": "懒人沙发 Cones", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-16T07:39:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052343496PFEfSLMjUR1DeJQ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t驻扎在伦敦的德国设计师 Jule Waibel 日前推出了一款懒人沙发 Cones，100% 羊毛制成，呈三维立体的褶皱形式，像是一颗蹲坐在地面上的松果，并赋予其一系列能够代表秋天的颜色。Jule Waibel 解释说，这次用来做褶皱的热蒸气工艺在很多工厂已经逐渐消失，是个很古老的工艺，很久之前用来做百褶裙的。这是一个很灵活，又扎实的可以适用于人的身体的结构，Jule Waibel 希望人们能够体验认识到 Cones 的美观与舒适性。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234346YjAUc02gLfPJTtae.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234346xJBSYrjFmA1X2P0w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052343472OqHiubChkyY7lrU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523434740NgQyBPeKVU8OA7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234348Ez2LnC0QPUtMVxRv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}